<item>
            <title>[LU-17021] ksnr_max_conns is used before it is set</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17021</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In ksocknal_add_peer, ksnr_max_conns is set but only after it is used in ksocknal_associate_cb_conn_locked called from ksocknal_add_conn_cb_locked.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems it could lead to bad ksnr_connected value.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
